HEADWORD: Respiratory
<hw>Re*spir"a*to*ry</hw> <pr>(r?*sp?r"?*t?*r? ⟦or⟧ r?s"p?*r?-)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to
